{"tid":1220011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港眾志成員美孚站跪求呼籲罷工　市民不滿阻返工","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:58:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7c217265077903c046a63b8999162af22a59132c","tid":1220011,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190614/photo/bkn-20190614093308055-0614_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190614100834\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190614%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190614093308055-0614_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190614100834&h=cfb916d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(香港眾志 fb)<br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》一事引起牽連大波，由百萬人遊行到衝擊立法會，近日再有市民發起不合作運動，阻礙港鐵運作以表達不滿。政黨香港眾志約7名成員今早(14日)到港鐵美孚站，拉起聲稱的「罷工迫擊線」，呼籲香港市民以罷工罷課，反對逃犯條例修訂，有市民批評他們阻礙上班。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志早前曾到中環站請願，以同樣方式阻礙市民上班，以呼籲港人參與罷工，今早再到美孚站內前往荃灣線的位置，成員一同跪地並手持「罷課罷工救港」的標語，及高叫「加入罷工」，前往上班的市民只能繞過示威者繼續前行，現場有最少5名港鐵職員在場維持秩序，另有約8名警員在場戒備。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190614/bkn-20190614093308055-0614_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190614%2Fbkn-20190614093308055-0614_00822_001.html&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWEBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=e14d2189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190614/bkn-20190614093308055-0614_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5099d8680db1f3f2abe683869d03a072e91fef62","tid":1220011,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae3cf5abfdd1bc98c8c16ef667132378f4dd767","tid":1220011,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:35:20.000Z","msg":"粉報，不意外"},{"pid":"bdae055901e4e10573d61a58e39bad1087f3ba4d","tid":1220011,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201